fiesta-can-bridge (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Non-blocking socket I/O with selectors.
  * Queue-based MQTT publishing via dedicated worker thread.
  * Decoders for 0x201 (RPM/speed/gas), 0x360 (brake), 0x420 (coolant+brake), 0x428 (battery).
  * WiCAN auto-discovery via dnsmasq lease file.
  * systemd service: can-bridge.service.

 -- semtex <semtex@users.noreply.github.com>  Mon, 16 Mar 2026 17:53:00 +0000
